Bot.,,,comb. nov.,37(3): 628,,,,,,true,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,2012 [25 Jun 2012],[25 Jun 2012],,,"Protologue (Basionym, synonymy & Remarks): Maranta albertii Pynaert & Van Geert in ? Calathea albertii (Pynaert & Van Geert) L. H. Bailey & Raffill in L. H. Bailey, Stand. Cycl. Hort. 2: 621. 1914.  Bailey and Rafill stated that their name was based on Maranta albertii Pynaert & Van Geert, but did not mention where that name had been published. IPNI does not include Maranta albertii or Calathea albertii. Govaerts and Kennedy (2012) do not provide a reference for the presumed basionym Maranta albertii either. Given this unusual situation we have chosen to follow the citation provided by Govaerts and Kennedy (2012), but further investigation is warranted. IPNI (dt. 18 July 2012) indexed Maranta albertii Pynaert & Van Geert (in Rev. Hort. Belge Étrangère 32: 20, 146. 1906) and flagged it as not validly published. doi:10.1600/036364412X648571",,,,,,,false,true,,,,
